s, and semantic patterns.<\/p>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex\">\r\n                    <div class=\"card h-100 w-100\">\r\n                        <div class=\"card-top understandable\"><\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"card-body d-flex flex-column\">\r\n                            <h3 class=\"card-title h6 fw-bold text-uppercase\"><span class=\"icon-container understandable me-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-journal-check me-2\"><\/i><\/span>WCAG Reference<\/h3>\r\n                            <hr class=\"my-2\"\/>\r\n                            <p class=\"card-text text-muted flex-grow-1\">Browse WCAG 2.1 success criteria by principle and conformance level.<\/p>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex\">\r\n                    <div class=\"card h-100 w-100\">\r\n                        <div class=\"card-top robust\"><\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"card-body d-flex flex-column\">\r\n                            <h3 class=\"card-title h6 fw-bold text-uppercase\"><span class=\"icon-container robust me-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-funnel me-2\"><\/i><\/span>Focused Filters<\/h3>\r\n                            <hr class=\"my-2\"\/>\r\n                            <p class=\"card-text text-muted flex-grow-1\">Filter guidelines by level or principle to focus on the most relevant issues.<\/p>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"row g-4 mb-5\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-lg-6 d-flex\">\r\n                    <div class=\"card h-100 w-100\">\r\n                        <div class=\"card-top operable\"><\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"card-body d-flex flex-column\">\r\n                            <h3 class=\"card-title h6 fw-bold text-uppercase\"><span class=\"icon-container operable me-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-diagram-3 me-2\"><\/i><\/span>How It Works<\/h3>\r\n                            <hr class=\"my-2\"\/>\r\n                            <ul class=\"list-unstyled text-muted mb-0\">\r\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Choose a URL or paste HTML code.<\/li>\r\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Run the scan or analysis to find issues.<\/li>\r\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Review related WCAG 2.1 guidance.<\/li>\r\n                                <li><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Apply fixes and re-check your page.<\/li>\r\n                            <\/ul>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-lg-6 d-flex\">\r\n                    <div class=\"card h-100 w-100\">\r\n                        <div class=\"card-top understandable\"><\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"card-body d-flex flex-column\">\r\n                            <h3 class=\"card-title h6 fw-bold text-uppercase\"><span class=\"icon-container understandable me-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-people me-2\"><\/i><\/span>Who It Is For<\/h3>\r\n                            <hr class=\"my-2\"\/>\r\n                            <ul class=\"list-unstyled text-muted mb-0\">\r\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Students and educators learning accessibility.<\/li>\r\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Designers and developers building inclusive UI.<\/li>\r\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-circle me-2\"><\/i>Project teams doing quick quality checks.<\/li>\r\n                            